Federal University Otuoke Admits 2,603 Students For 2017/2018. The Federal University Otuoke has Admitted 2,603 Students for the 2017/2018 academic session. Prof Accra Jaja the Vice-Chancellor of Federal University, Otuoke, Bayelsa State made this known on Saturday at the 7th matriculation ceremony of the institution that 2,602 students were admitted into academic programmes in six faculties … The post Federal University Otuoke Admits 2,603 Students For 2017/2018. appeared first on Students Nigeria. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from Students Nigeria. Click here to read the full text on the original website.